OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776355854
OL,3,CMan found stabbed to death in garden
OL,4,Cnamed as housemate charged with his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,8,Fafter his housemate was found stabbed
OL,9,Fin a Filton garden.
OL,11,FZack Coughlan, 23, was arrested on
OL,12,FSunday 12 April and has been charged
OL,13,Fwith the murder of 21-year-old Jamie
OL,14,FCollins.
OL,16,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,17,Fgarden at the rear of the property in
OL,18,FCleve Road in the early hours of
OL,19,FThursday 9 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
