PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776355854
OL,3,CMan found stabbed to death in garden
OL,4,Cnamed as housemate charged with his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FBoth men lived together in a house
OL,8,Fshare.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector, Lucy
OL,11,FEdgeworth, of the Major Crime
OL,12,FInvestigation Team, said: "The Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service has authorised a
OL,14,Fmurder charge against Zack Coughlan.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
