FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776355854
OL,3,CMan found stabbed to death in garden
OL,4,Cnamed as housemate charged with his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with Jamie's family
OL,8,Fat this hugely difficult time and
OL,9,Fspecially-trained officers are
OL,10,Foffering them support and keeping them
OL,11,Fregularly updated with our
OL,12,Finvestigation. We would politely ask
OL,13,Fpeople continue to respect their
OL,14,Fprivacy."
OL,16,FCoughlan appeared at Bristol
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court today (Tuesday 14
OL,18,FApril) and has been remanded in
OL,19,Fcustody.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
