PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776355854
OL,3,CMan found stabbed to death in garden
OL,4,Cnamed as housemate charged with his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHe is due to appear at Bristol Crown
OL,8,FCourt tomorrow morning for a
OL,9,Fpreliminary hearing.
OL,11,FDCI Edgeworth added: "People who knew
OL,12,FJamie will be understandably shocked
OL,13,Fand hugely saddened to learn of what
OL,14,Fhas happened.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
