PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776355854
OL,3,CMan found stabbed to death in garden
OL,4,Cnamed as housemate charged with his
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Neighbourhood officers have been
OL,8,Fcarrying out high-visibility patrols
OL,9,Fin the area over recent days and are
OL,10,Fworking closely with staff at the
OL,11,FUniversity of the West of England,
OL,12,Fwhere both men were students, to
OL,13,Fensure support is in place for those
OL,14,Fwho need it.
OL,16,F"Further enquiries are planned in the
OL,17,Farea around Cleve Road over the coming
OL,18,Fdays. We are grateful to people living
OL,19,Fin the area for their patience and
OL,20,Funderstanding while we continue to
OL,21,Fcarry out this investigative work."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU}D@cO]
